{{Top|canon=Mummery}}
'''Mummergy''' was a type of strong-smelling [[Plant/Legends|plant]] used to make [[Alcohol/Legends|liquor]] and as a type of [[Spice/Legends|spice]]. [[Wuher/Legends|Wuher]] used it to create a drink for [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba the Hutt]]. The [[Mummers]] took their name from the plant.

